title: UROTSUKIDOJI_DISCA.ISO
description:
The Perfect Collection from Anime 18 is the only English friendly uncut version of the first OVA available outside Japan. 

I ripped these two disks as ISO exactly as they were in the box.

This is very hard to find, so thought i would push it up before i sold the original dvds.

IMDB does not list the uncut version, so the IMDB link is only provided as a basic reference.

Disk two will go up after this one seeds awhile as i have very limited upload here in Thailand

Tentacle Porn at its best
